{"tid":2224470,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！12被送中手足！鹽田逮捕喬映瑜及鄧榮然！一個也不能少！","createTime":"2020-09-30T13:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T16:46:28.000Z","uid":31166,"like":51,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"9502423990a9f2ffda2fc8941b1a9ab7e041b3d7","tid":2224470,"uid":31166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T13:36:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">呢個中秋真係&hellip;個也不能少啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推爆佢呀大家，就算做啲嘢好似冇乜用都要繼續做！<br />\n<br />\n關於Moon有媒體資料指係一個患有嚴重抑鬱既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球聯署要求中國政府送返12名被捕港人<br />\nGlobal Petition: Immediate Return<br />\nof the 12 HK Detainees from Mainland China!<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/save12youthspetitions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fsave12youthspetitions&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyi2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=2a958181\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/save12youthspetitions</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/09/30/213300_c336f5c4d97392dc52338efed37547dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F09%2F30%2F213300_c336f5c4d97392dc52338efed37547dd.png&h=fe7ae399&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/09/30/213305_ae1a4d5e34186e39efa2d6222abacec5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F09%2F30%2F213305_ae1a4d5e34186e39efa2d6222abacec5.jpeg&h=e969dad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#Breaking On the eve of #midautumnfestival&nbsp;, a day of family reunion, #Chinese prosecutors just approved the arrest of #12hkyouths. <br />\n<br />\n1. Two, Tang &amp; Quinn Moon, are accused of &ldquo;organizing illegal border crossing&rdquo; while the other 10 are alleged of &ldquo;illegal border crossing.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=